tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE demographic_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR,
    ethnicity VARCHAR,
    income INT,
    zip_code VARCHAR,
    health_condition VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE DemographicData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR,
    ethnicity VARCHAR,
    risk_factor VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE demographics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
    income FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE health_conditions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    condition_name VARCHAR(100),
    diagnosis_date DATE,
    severity VARCHAR(20),
    patient_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE interventions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    intervention_name VARCHAR(100),
    target_group VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE population_demographics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    population_id INT,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
    city VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE intervention_tracking (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    intervention_id INT,
    population_id INT,
    intervention_date DATE,
    success_rate FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE demographics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR,
    ethnicity VARCHAR,
    income INT
);

CREATE TABLE health_conditions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    condition VARCHAR,
    diagnosis_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES demographics(id)
);

CREATE TABLE interventions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    intervention_name VARCHAR,
    target_population VARCHAR,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE patient_health (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    health_status VARCHAR,
    record_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES demographics(id)
);

CREATE TABLE intervention_logs (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    intervention_id INT,
    patient_id INT,
    log_date DATE,
    success BOOLEAN,
    FOREIGN KEY (intervention_id) REFERENCES interventions(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES demographics(id)
);
